{
  "id": "plot_ch1_cloud_rift",
  "chapter_id": "ch1",
  "title": "界桥动荡",
  "description": "云海之夜，界桥裂缝短暂扩大，雾川抵御来袭的灵兽。",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "start",
      "speaker": "旁白",
      "text": "深夜，界桥裂缝短暂扩大。大量灵兽从裂缝中涌出。",
      "next_node_id": "start2",
      "is_cutscene": true,
      "cloud_delta": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "start2",
      "speaker": "雾川",
      "text": "有敌袭。是灵界的低级灵兽，被某种力量驱使着攻击山庄。",
      "next_node_id": "start3",
      "is_cutscene": true,
      "cloud_delta": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "start3",
      "speaker": "老槐",
      "text": "孩子，快躲进屋里！",
      "next_node_id": "start4",
      "is_cutscene": true,
      "cloud_delta": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "start4",
      "speaker": "雾川",
      "text": "保护好自己。今晚……可能会很危险。",
      "next_node_id": "choice",
      "is_cutscene": true,
      "cloud_delta": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "choice",
      "speaker": "旁白",
      "text": "玩家可以选择行动方式。",
      "choices": [
        { "id": "fight", "text": "和云狐一起战斗", "next": "fight_start" },
        { "id": "command", "text": "指挥灵兽作战", "next": "command_start" }
      ],
      "is_cutscene": false,
      "cloud_delta": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "fight_start",
      "speaker": "雾川",
      "text": "……好。跟我来。灵兽的战斗和人类不同，它们靠灵气和默契来战斗。信任它，和它配合，你们一定能赢。",
      "next_node_id": "fight_win",
      "is_cutscene": true,
      "cloud_delta": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "fight_win",
      "speaker": "雾川",
      "text": "不错……你们的配合很好。记住今晚的战斗。以后，会有更大的挑战等着你。",
      "next_node_id": "end",
      "is_cutscene": true,
      "choice_effects": [{ "flag_to_set": "ch1_fought_with_beast" }],
      "cloud_delta": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "command_start",
      "speaker": "老槐",
      "text": "好！你来指挥，我来辅助！",
      "next_node_id": "command_win",
      "is_cutscene": true,
      "cloud_delta": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "command_win",
      "speaker": "老槐",
      "text": "干得好！你的指挥能力很强。",
      "next_node_id": "end",
      "is_cutscene": true,
      "choice_effects": [{ "flag_to_set": "ch1_commanded_beast" }],
      "cloud_delta": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "end",
      "speaker": "旁白",
      "text": "经过一夜的奋战，来袭的灵兽被成功击退。黎明到来，云海渐渐消散。",
      "next_node_id": "end2",
      "is_cutscene": true,
      "cloud_delta": +10
    },
    {
      "id": "end2",
      "speaker": "老槐",
      "text": "孩子，今晚你做得很好。你没有退缩，和大家一起保护了山庄。这就是守护者的精神。继续努力吧，第一章的考验……你通过了。",
      "next_node_id": "",
      "is_cutscene": true,
      "cloud_delta": 0
    }
  ],
  "start_node_id": "start",
